---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Bits And Bytes IT Solutions"
  description="Privacy policy for Bits And Bytes IT Solutions."
>
  <section class="space-y-5">
    <p class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-cyan-200/30 bg-cyan-200/10 px-4 py-1 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-cyan-100">
      Legal
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-white md:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-300">
      This policy explains how Bits And Bytes IT Solutions collects, uses, and protects personal information when you use our website or contact us about services.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Last updated: July 16, 2026</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 grid gap-4">
    <article class="glass-card">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-slate-300">
        <li>Contact details such as your name, email address, and company name.</li>
        <li>Project details you provide through forms, calls, or email communication.</li>
        <li>Basic website usage data (for example, pages viewed and referral source).</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="glass-card">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">How We Use Information</h2>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-slate-300">
        <li>To respond to inquiries and provide service proposals or estimates.</li>
        <li>To deliver contracted services and communicate project updates.</li>
        <li>To improve website content, offerings, and user experience.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="glass-card">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Data Sharing</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">
        We do not sell your personal data. Information may be shared only with trusted service providers involved in hosting, communication, analytics, or project delivery under appropriate confidentiality safeguards.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="glass-card">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-300">
        You may request access, correction, or deletion of your personal data at any time. To make a request, contact us at hello@bitsandbytesitsolutions.com.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
